    "body": "That's a good question. If you inspect `$matches` in a brand new PS session, it is actually null. That seems to indicate to me that it's not an automatic variable, just that it's set in the current scope when `-match` is used.\r\n\r\nNot an exhaustive investigation, but that's my bet until I've had time to look through the code üòÅ ",
